{"type": "article", "id": 26921, "title": "Gucci 发布男装度假系列，以及，推荐台湾买手店 Ne.Sense｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-17T10:58:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8773, "name": "海洋"}, {"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 23070, "name": "粉红"}, {"id": 1130, "name": "手表"}, {"id": 24323, "name": "法式简约"}, {"id": 615, "name": "旧金山"}, {"id": 9642, "name": "门店"}, {"id": 27723, "name": "四月"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 12407, "name": "兰芝"}, {"id": 14878, "name": "Reformation"}, {"id": 17504, "name": "A.P.C."}, {"id": 949, "name": "DVF"}, {"id": 2910, "name": "Hugo Boss"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 2041, "name": "Jimmy Choo"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142347q7cU4FBaPjbGEeQn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/5/16/11682618/jonathan-saunders-diane-von-furstenberg\"><b>Jonathan Saunders 担任 DVF 创意总监</b></a>｜ 38 岁的苏格兰设计师 Jonathan Saunders 担任 Diane Von Furstenberg 创意总监，即刻生效。Diane Von Furstenberg 在声明中对 Jonathan 在色彩、印花方面的才华及设计风格给予肯定。此前，Jonathan 一直被认为可能会接替 Raf Simons 成为 Dior 的创意总监。2003 年 Jonathan Saunders 在伦敦建立自己的个人品牌，2015 年因个人原因离开。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Cold-spring-pushes-H-M-April-sales-below-forecast,693175.html#.VzoCaoQrJQY\"><b>寒春令 H&amp;M 四月销售额低于预期</b></a>｜世界第二大快时尚巨头 H&amp;M 近日宣布四月销售额增长稍低于预期，仅比去年同期获得 5% 的增长，低于路透社 9% 的预期。几大关键市场的寒冷天气导致销售额遭遇一定压力。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/eyewear/jimmy-choo-safilo-extend-license-launch-men-collection-10431001/\"><b>Safilo 与 Jimmy Choo 继续合作眼镜生产</b></a>｜Safilo 集团日前宣布与 Jimmy Choo 续约，将继续为其生产及分销旗下眼镜系列，合约更新至 2023 年 12 月 31 日。同时将新增 Jimmy Choo 男士眼镜系列，2018 年 1 月起将作为首个胶囊系列出现在品牌门店及精品眼镜店内。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/menswear-news/designer-luxury/hugo-boss-mark-langer-ceo-claus-dietrich-lahrs10430979-10430979/\"><b>Hugo Boss 原首席财政官担任 CEO</b></a>｜德国品牌 Hugo Boss 近日宣布其首席财政官 Mark Langer 将担任集团 CEO 的职位，Langer 已加入 Hugo Boss 长达 13 年。而截至 3 月 31 日的一季度，公司净收益猛跌了 49%，营业收益下跌了 48% ，集团销售额也减少了 4%。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Salvatore-Ferragamo-reopens-flagship-store-in-Avenue-Montaigne-Paris,693296.html#.Vzp9gYQrJQY\"><b>菲拉格慕重开巴黎蒙田大道旗舰店</b></a>｜意大利奢侈品牌 Salvatore Ferragamo 更新其主要门店，最近重开的一家是位于蒙田大道的巴黎旗舰店，成为品牌在欧洲最大的一家门店，将陈列 Salvatore Ferragamo 从男女装到配饰的全线产品。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Gucci 发布 2017 男装度假系列，87 套 looks，<a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/13436595/gucci-mens-cruise-2017/\">更多图片可点击这里</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142322TVd8aPq2LkN47fK0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45864662\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142323nZfdpse3IL5U6Jor.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44956413\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142324AjzSiWnH2CMLf6k0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45149254\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142325Z9fvKTQUJRIVcbjq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45611867\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021423259BMeKGvbsnCYT03l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142326NBzvVuqA7jEpTDIw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44956413\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142326xgQoLZS5jWXdspD6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44582814\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/reforamtion-pink-collection/\">Reformation 夏季系列</a>，主打深浅不一的粉红系：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021423276NmkZrUu4eY7a1sD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142328NwPTkS6iIyAXc2fG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142329eMfEkvuXo8tSIsW6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142329lh2Jitvx3zLbKOYp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142330RQas4fHbPD37xLEB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">一向走法式简约路线的品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/apc-san-francisco-shop\">A.P.C. 近日在旧金山开了家新门店</a>，内部狭长的空间延续品牌极简和舒适的设计风格：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142331gjuIElC6nGXZOFir.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142331ZEdy0oMWHwsnDFf8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142332Rru9oOTCvGbZQjA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142333KumN5PSQ9VOHTa7s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142333JvusHRtZQTcV5Phj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">台湾买手店 Ne.Sense 拍摄了其<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/05/14/ne-sense-ss16-memo-lookbook/#slide-4\">男装夏日 lookbook</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142334EaiTytMcS0Z5nfOv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142335LGSs4W0B7la8YgUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142336gLanPbCRGfI7ci4N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142338y6t9lxdMFvj4VbKH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142338gfM7S5ExwLknd2ui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142339IusqtlPrLxi526ow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142340UmLhE4AoqwS3Qy8Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142340tWLPqw8IzyBRpEsF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">韩国美妆品牌<a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/keep-cool-with-laneiges-summer-makeup-collection/\">兰芝（ Laneige）推出夏季航海主题彩妆系列</a>，海军条纹的包装设计：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142341c7L5Z0O4HVMUbhiv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142342btjFoVJIXrzD1RAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021423429hA0y4CvWp8kOPnc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142343D2JXq7sVoxNE41Wk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"> Chanel 推出名为 <a href=\"http://bagaholicboy.com/2016/05/chanel-boyfriend-black-dial-steel-watch-collection/\">Boyfriend 的系列黑色手表</a>，钢制表面及黑色皮质表带呈现简约造型：<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142343gCUAIzmyicpD9fS4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142346ueAIhv438KQbmBtE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}